---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Patent Analyzer | Steve Jevon Rahardjo" description="AI-Powered Patent Document Analysis System using LLMs and RAG.">
  <div class="container page">
    <a href="/projects" class="back-link">← Back to Projects</a>
    
    <article class="project-detail">
      <header class="project-detail-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">Patent Analyzer</h1>
        <p class="project-subtitle">AI-Powered Patent Document Analysis System</p>
      </header>

      <section class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text">
          The Patent Analysis System is an intelligent platform designed to analyze and interact with
          patent documents using advanced natural language processing and machine learning techniques.
        </p>
        <p class="text">
          The system leverages vector databases, semantic search, and large language models to provide
          accurate, context-aware responses to queries about patent content.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>PDF Upload - Process patent documents in PDF format</li>
          <li>Vector Embeddings - Convert patent text to semantic vectors</li>
          <li>Q{"&"}A Chatbot - Ask questions and get intelligent answers</li>
          <li>Topic Classification - Automatic categorization of patents</li>
          <li>TRIZ Analysis - Extract innovation principles from claims</li>
          <li>Dockerized - Easy deployment with Docker Compose</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Architecture</h2>
        <p class="text">The system consists of multiple services:</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Backend API - FastAPI server handling document processing</li>
          <li>Vector Database - Storage for semantic embeddings</li>
          <li>LLM Service - Language model for question answering</li>
          <li>Frontend - React-based UI for interaction</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="project-section">
        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Tech Stack</h2>
        <div class="project-tech">
          <span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">FastAPI</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">NLP</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Vector DB</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">Docker</span>
          <span class="tech-tag">React</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .project-detail {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .project-detail-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .project-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .feature-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .project-tech {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tech-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
</style>
